          },

          {
            "type": "list",
            "text": [
              "Word association is a way to study how people connect words with each other. For example, if someone hears the word \"dog,\" they might associate it with \"cat\" or \"bark.\"",
              "Word association is the way in which our brain connects different words with each other. ",
              "By knowing how people connect different words, we can choose our words more carefully to make sure we're understood. "
